README for cytoscape:  how to build, test and run
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------
# $Revision$
# $Date$
# $Author$
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------


PREREQUISITES
--------------
junit 3.7   (or later)
LEDA 4.1
cppunit 1.5.5 (or later)

DEFINE
------

  environment variable   sample value
  --------------------   ----------------
   LEDA_HOME:            /local/LEDA-4.1
   CPPUNIT_HOME:         /local/cppunit
   LD_LIBRARY_PATH       /usr/lib:/local/LEDA-4.1:/local/cppunit

TO BUILD
--------
define your java CLASSPATH to include at least

    <full-path-to-current-directory>/cytoscape.aux.jar
    <full-path-to-immediate-parent-directory>
    <full-path-to-junit.jar>


in the current directory (<someDirectory>/cytoscape)

  make
  make test
  make run0
